## VM arguments for TPS Kanban

## Name of the node
-name tps_kanban@127.0.0.1

## Cookie for distributed erlang
-setcookie tps_kanban_secret_cookie

## Enable kernel poll threads
+K true

## Number of async threads
+A 256

## Max number of ports
-env ERL_MAX_PORTS 65536

## Heartbeat interval
-heart

## Process flag settings
+P 262144

## Memory allocation strategy
+MMmcs 50
